title: Ranch oyster crackers
directions: In a large mixing bowl, combine first 5 ingredients and mix well. Stir in oyster crackers mix to coat. Pour crackers onto a large cookie sheet.
Bake 15 minutes, stirring every 5 minutes or so.
Cool and add to a covered container.
ingredients: 1 t dried dill weed (or to your taste)
1/2 t garlic powder (or to your taste)
